{"tid":2337993,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"朋友","createTime":"2020-12-23T16:39:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-24T02:31:24.000Z","uid":387042,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4bd2a87a1957be8b028a646da8f4bdca663b2cd6","tid":2337993,"uid":387042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T16:39:06.000Z","msg":"人越大身邊啲朋友就越嚟越少<br />\n係就係話朋友貴精不貴多，雖然身邊仲有幾個真心朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />識咗好多年都仲係會暢所欲言，一齊陪伴大家成長，但身邊都係酒肉朋友較多。無可否認，酒肉朋友都有佢嘅位置，但有時候真係唔知應唔應該繼續，唔想失去任何一個朋友，想多個人了解自己，但到頭來都係為咗比佢消磨時間。見到人哋好多朋友，一齊慶祝聖誕，自己就毒撚係屋企過<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />返學online上堂又識唔到人，完sem都唔知點解人地可以識到一堆朋友，自己就一個人。<br />\n好想擴大自己社交圈子，但唔成功，覺得自己好孤獨，由其喺夜晚，一個人聽住歌，望住天花板，思考人生，點解人生咁多嘢煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/south_bear.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><a href=\"https://youtu.be/bD12C-mGth4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FbD12C-mGth4&d=djscsuFvXcghIMf2lgFVpzcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=39e69934\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/bD12C-mGth4</a>"},{"pid":"b02f35d750ea2974f2a2dc27c2de43a3113a70a3","tid":2337993,"uid":387042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T16:42:37.000Z","msg":"又訓唔著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c728e5d9f67522c955cf2a1728479c9c21e8bcd4","tid":2337993,"uid":9392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T16:52:45.000Z","msg":"朋友兄弟都係過客"},{"pid":"fb5d98c36d3426903f1a01da15dc69205cf3bc75","tid":2337993,"uid":387042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c728e5d9f67522c955cf2a1728479c9c21e8bcd4","tid":2337993,"uid":9392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T16:52:45.000Z","msg":"朋友兄弟都係過客"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T17:04:32.000Z","msg":"我知<br />\n但唔想身邊嘅人走曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1612680ae8c7845d151cbdecfb2dea56902eb73f","tid":2337993,"uid":371893,"like":0,"dislike"